        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="section-header__desc">
          Completing the CPR and AED certification directly contributed to my development as a Medical Expert by strengthening clinical judgment, procedural skills, and evidence-based approach to emergency care.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Certificate preview card -->
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: var(--sp-xl); margin-bottom: var(--sp-2xl); align-items: start;" class="fade-up" id="cpr-cert-grid">
        <div>
          <div style="background: var(--c-card); border: 1px solid var(--c-border); border-radius: var(--r-xl); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--sh-card);">
            <div style="background: var(--c-text); padding: var(--sp-md) var(--sp-lg); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--sp-sm);">
              <div style="width: 40px; height: 40px; background: var(--c-secondary); border-radius: var(--r-md); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0;">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p style="color: #fff; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600;">Certificate of Completion</p>
                <p style="color: rgba(255,247,245,0.55); font-size: 0.78rem;">Dubai Health Authority · Dubai Heart Safe City Programme</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <iframe
              src="assets/certificate-cpr-aed.pdf"
              title="CPR AED Certificate"
              style="width: 100%; height: 380px; border: none; display: block; background: var(--c-card);">
