            </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="heading-md" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-md);">Training Overview</p>
          <p class="body-md" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-md);">
            The training offered a structured blend of theory and hands-on practice, allowing me to integrate foundational scientific knowledge with practical competencies essential for managing life-threatening situations.
          </p>
          <p class="body-md" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-lg);">
            Engaging with real-time simulations helped me understand the physiological basis of cardiac arrest, the importance of timely intervention, and the impact of high-quality chest compressions on patient outcomes.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem;">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: var(--c-accent); border-radius: var(--r-md); border: 1px solid var(--c-border);">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c-secondary)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--c-text);">Dubai Health Authority – Nationally Recognised</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: var(--c-accent); border-radius: var(--r-md); border: 1px solid var(--c-border);">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c-secondary)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--c-text);">Hands-on CPR &amp; AED simulation training</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: var(--c-accent); border-radius: var(--r-md); border: 1px solid var(--c-border);">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c-secondary)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--c-text);">Evidence-based protocol application</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: var(--c-accent); border-radius: var(--r-md); border: 1px solid var(--c-border);">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c-secondary)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
