                  <p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-text); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Observe</p>
                  <p style="font-size: 0.825rem; color: var(--c-muted); line-height: 1.6;">Engage actively with every clinical scenario, noting patterns, decisions, and outcomes without judgement.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--sp-sm);">
                <div style="width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--c-secondary); border-radius: var(--r-md); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;">2</div>
